{
  "texts": [
    "Similarly, the proven effectiveness of language processing in marketing since the chatbot era (e.g., (Cheng and Jiang 2022)) motivates professionals to explore ChatGPT's lucrative applications.",
    "The high volume of positive tweets endorsing ChatGPT's marketing usefulness reflects this optimism.",
    "Furthermore, Prompt Engineering, the art of crafting optimal inputs for ChatGPT, garnered mainly positive sentiment, likely due to its increasing importance across diverse professions.",
    "While the sentiment towards ChatGPT remained positive across Education, Healthcare, Prompt Engineering, Art, Marketing, and Writing, its temporal evolution varied.",
    "For Education, Healthcare, Prompt Engineering, and Art, the percentage of positive tweets increased while that of negative tweets decreased over time."
  ]
}